这场纷争的真相，值得我们继续关注和探讨。 震撼！李明德离别信曝光，直指马天宇耍大牌引剧组风波！_质疑_何在_真相"},"attached_info":"CkEIyZTIgvnhntobEAMaCTExMjcxOTI5NyCsx+S7BjAAOLcEQBRyCjg3MTM5MTM3Mjd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"5.7 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-b38ae886d068039015cae67b308f9b77_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"21_1736068762.994988","card_id":"Q_8630806031","target":{"id":8630806031,"title":"在酒席中不想喝酒，请问如何礼貌拒绝？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/8630806031","type":"question","created":1735906183,"answer_count":81,"follower_count":143,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[7766],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"每次出去应酬，有时候身体不舒服，不想喝酒，但是平时别人都知道自己会喝酒，来来回回解释了很久，就是不知道如何拒绝喝酒。"},"attached_info":"CkEIyZTIgvnhntobEAMaCTExMjcwMjcwMSCHp9+7BjAAOI8BQBVyCjg2MzA4MDYwMzF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"5.6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-807e743644fccdb099e1f0d348ca81ef_1440w.webp"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"22_1736068762.995249","card_id":"Q_8553759375","target":{"id":8553759375,"title":"如何评价《一人之下》漫画700（740）话？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/8553759375","type":"question","created":1735834588,"answer_count":90,"follower_count":107,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[125,169573],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkAIyZTIgvnhntobEAMaCTExMjY4NzE5OSDc99q7BjAAOGtAFnIKODU1Mzc1OTM3NXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"4.6 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-7b61913f771bd2cf31e207bd177822fb_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_lis